OL,4,G1800FClangers
OL,5,     GSweet Music. Stop-motion
OL,6,     Ganimation. A radio falls out of
OL,7,     Gthe sky. Tiny, Small and Baby
OL,8,     GSoup Dragon don't know what it is
OL,9,     Gand are fascinated by the sounds
OL,10,     Gthat come from it.
OL,11,G1810FBeddyByes
OL,12,     GFriend Song. MeMo and BaBa listen
OL,13,     Gto the beautiful sounds that
OL,14,     Gtheir friends are making all
OL,15,     Garound them. MeMo and BaBa use
OL,16,     Gthose sounds to create a
OL,17,     Gwonderful friendship song.
